clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我夠知sony啲e-mount鏡差不多全部扭fo都係電子驅動<br />\n<br />\n咁唔係個個都識自己MF 俾番相應意見姐<br />\n<br />\n之前試過攞支batis 85扭撚死個cam assist之後無再用e-mount鏡 除非要AF</blockquote><br />\n唔明喎，咁電子驅動咪即係自動對焦囉？"},{"pid":"94179edd6a8be7b9d061f2b96267fe181cfc5874","tid":209070,"uid":29291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T21:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>拍片想要自動對焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只有一個選擇： sony原廠e mount鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍片af用咩野接環都假</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我夠知sony啲e-mount鏡差不多全部扭fo都係電子驅動<br />\n<br />\n咁唔係個個都識自己MF 俾番相應意見姐<br />\n<br />\n之前試過攞支batis 85扭撚死個cam assist之後無再用e-mount鏡 除非要AF</blockquote><br />\n唔明喎，咁電子驅動咪即係自動對焦囉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既 <br />\n<br />\n其實講緊個對焦環點樣驅動塊鏡片做focus <br />\n<br />\n傳統鏡頭係機械控制 你扭個對焦環幾快幾慢佢都係直接咁驅動塊鏡片 唔會因爲你快慢唔同而影響到個對焦行程<br />\n<br />\n但e-mount鏡個對焦環並唔係機械而係線性傳動 即係話你扭果陣並唔係直接控制 而係俾signal個摩打再去轉個focus 所以個反應差得多"}]}